                    <span>This book, with an obvious nod to Strunk and White (which it surpasses), lists 67 principles of good writing, with about two pages each of details and examples. It's on the short list of recommended resources in my book The McGraw-Hill 36-Hour Course in Business Writing and Communication.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A wise investment</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
