                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2001-04-25</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>If you write letters, emails, business proposals or marketing plans, this book will be useful to you.  It is very easy to follow.  The book offers a number of suggestions for writing clearly and with style, and explains each point in detail.  I used this book for a graduate level class, but it would be useful to anyone!</span>
                  
